Interface SocialContract.BaseSyncColumns

All Known Implementing Classes:

Enclosing class:
SocialContract
public static interface SocialContract.BaseSyncColumns

These columns are privately used by sync adapters and should not be used by applications. Sync adapters can choose to use them in any way they want. Note: This interface is based on Android class CalendarContract.

Author:
Babak Farshchian
